    # mc "Charles is a good name, but a little stuffy. {w}We could call him [d17s06_teddy_name!t]."
    mc "查尔斯是个好名字，但有点古板。{w}我们可以叫他[d17s06_teddy_name!t]."

# game/code/d17/d17s06dd.rpy:101
